  "commit_message": "fix: harden smtp-connection low-severity issues\n\nA pass over the low-severity items from the smtp-connection review:\n\n- _destroy(): keep the public `destroyed` flag in sync with the private state (it was documented but never updated)\n- reset(): add the login()/send() destroyed-guard so the callback errors instead of hanging on a dead connection\n- _onConnectionError(): attach TEARDOWN_NOOP before destroying the failed fallback socket (mirrors close()) so a late teardown error can't go unhandled\n-",
